nl.tue.fingerpaint.client.storage

Class ResultStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.fingerpaint.client.storage.ResultStorage

  • public class ResultStorage
extends Object
    Class that holds everything needed to store a mixing result. Can be JSONized using the ResultStorageJsonizer

    Group Fingerpaint
